				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\mathrm{K} \mathrm{Al}_{3} \mathrm{Si}_{3} \mathrm{O}_{8}$\end{document}) the analog chemical equation can be written with atomic K as one of the end products.

Analysis of observed ENA data from the Chandrayaan-1 mission showed that the directional ENA flux jENA(SZA,θ,φ)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
