				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$v_{\mathit{SW}} \approx 400$\end{document} km s−1) experience 10 to 20 of collisions to end up with a characteristic energy of about 100 eV. Fig. 19
